snippet.title: The Sailor’s Dream - November 6th
snippet.description:
A peaceful narrative experience, in which the only objective is to satisfy your curiosity.

Explore serene structures on dreamlike islands and piece together memories – some even existing beyond the screen of your device.

The Sailor’s Dream launches November 6th on iPhone, iPod touch and iPad.
